      "text": "Python File Open",
      "level": "h1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "File handling is an important part of any web application.",
      "html": "<p class=\"intro\">File handling is an important part of any web application.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "Python has several functions for creating, reading, updating, and deleting files.",
      "html": "<p class=\"intro\">Python has several functions for creating, reading, updating, and \ndeleting files.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "metadata": {
        "level": "h2"
      },
      "text": "File Handling",
      "level": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The key function for working with files in Python is the open() function.",
      "html": "<p>The key function for working with files in Python is the\n<code>open()</code> function.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The open() function takes two parameters; filename , and mode .",
      "html": "<p>The <code>open()</code> function takes two parameters;\n<em>filename</em>, and <em>mode</em>.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "There are four different methods (modes) for opening a file:",
      "html": "<p>There are four different methods (modes) for opening a file:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "unknown",
        "tryItLink": null,
        "syntaxHighlighting": [],
        "classList": [
          "w3-example"
        ],
        "isNotranslate": false
      },
      "code": "\"r\" - Read - Default value. Opens a file for reading, error if the file does not exist \"a\" - Append - Opens a file for appending, creates the file if it does not exist \"w\" - Write - Opens a file for writing, creates the file if it does not exist \"x\" - Create - Creates the specified file, returns an error if the file exists",
      "language": "unknown",
      "tryItLink": null,
      "syntax_highlighting_data": [],
      "class_list": [
        "w3-example"
      ],
      "is_notranslate": false
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "In addition you can specify if the file should be handled as binary or text mode",
      "html": "<p>In addition you can specify if the file should be handled as binary or text mode</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "unknown",
        "tryItLink": null,
        "syntaxHighlighting": [],
        "classList": [
          "w3-example"
        ],
        "isNotranslate": false
      },
      "code": "\"t\" - Text - Default value. Text mode \"b\" - Binary - Binary mode (e.g. images)",
      "language": "unknown",
      "tryItLink": null,
      "syntax_highlighting_data": [],
      "class_list": [
        "w3-example"
      ],
      "is_notranslate": false
    },
